cs.LO, cs.CC, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.DM

This paper deals with the classification of first-order formulas based on their quantifier resource, which is a topic in mathematical logic. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also uses game-theoretic techniques, which are often used in computational complexity theory (cs.CC) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study of finite structures is related to discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and the use of strategy compositions is related to algorithm design and analysis (cs.DS).
